{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-source-drupal7","description":"Gatsby source plugin for Drupal 7","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","gatsby-source-plugin"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"porkloin","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/ffe43600922d9dbc3068a44066642387"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/porkloin/gatsby-source-drupal7"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-source-drupal7\"><a href=\"#gatsby-source-drupal7\" aria-label=\"gatsby source drupal7 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-source-drupal7</h1>\n<p>A source plugin for Gatsby that pulls data from Drupal 7.</p>\n<p>This source plugin has been forked from <a href=\"https://github.com/gatsbyjs/gatsby/tree/master/packages/gatsby-source-drupal\">gatsby-source-drupal</a> to extend functionality\nto Drupal 7.</p>\n<h2 id=\"requirements\"><a href=\"#requirements\" aria-label=\"requirements permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Requirements:</h2>\n<p>Drupal 7 site with the following modules installed and enabled:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.drupal.org/project/restws\">restws</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.drupal.org/project/restws_resource_discovery\">restws<em>resource</em>discovery</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.drupal.org/project/uuid\">uuid</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install:</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-source-drupal7</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"configuration\"><a href=\"#configuration\" aria-label=\"configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Configuration:</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// In your gatsby-config.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: [\n    {\n      resolve: `gatsby-source-drupal7`,\n      options: {\n        baseUrl: `https://live-mydrupal7site.pantheonsite.io/`,\n        apiBase: `restws_resource.json`, // optional, defaults to `restws_resource.json`\n      },\n    },\n  ],\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"auth\"><a href=\"#auth\" aria-label=\"auth permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Auth:</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// In your gatsby-config.js\nmodule.exports = {\n  plugins: [\n    {\n      resolve: `gatsby-source-drupal7`,\n      options: {\n        baseUrl: `https://live-mydrupal7site.pantheonsite.io/`,\n        apiBase: `restws_resource.json`, // optional, defaults to `restws_resource.json`\n        basicAuth: {\n          username: process.env.BASIC_AUTH_USERNAME,\n          password: process.env.BASIC_AUTH_PASSWORD,\n        },\n      },\n    },\n  ],\n}</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"querying\"><a href=\"#querying\" aria-label=\"querying permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Querying:</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n  allNode {\n    edges {\n      node {\n        data {\n          title\n          created\n          body {\n            value\n          }\n        }\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>","timeToRead":1}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-source-drupal7/","id":"049acadd-ff34-57ef-b37a-ac102b6b7c8f","layout":"plugins"}}